snippet.title: Cube World: Explorers
snippet.description:
This video shows some footage of my game project 'Cube World'. It's still in development and not available yet. For more info check our homepage https://picroma.com and Twitter http://twitter.com/wol_lay

New features in this video:
- classes (warriors, rogues, rangers, mages)
- pet riding
- world map
- crafting
- skill trees
- boats

I'm planning to make more detailed videos about each class and their skills later. :)
